            <title><![CDATA[Clive Barker’s Hellraiser: Revival announced for PC and consoles]]></title>
            <link>https://www.thesixthaxis.com/2025/07/22/clive-barkers-hellraiser-revival-announced-for-pc-and-consoles/</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/clive-barker%E2%80%99s-hellraiser-revival-announced-for-pc-and-consoles.1249623/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div itemprop="text">
	
		<p><a href="https://www.thesixthaxis.com/tag/saber-interactive/">Saber Interactive</a> and Boss Team Games are bringing an iconic horror franchise back to life&nbsp; with Clive Barker’s Hellraiser: Revival, a single-player survival horror action game set in the flesh-ripping world of Hellraiser.&nbsp; They’ve also managed to persuade actor Doug Bradley to return to the role of Pinhead for the first time in nearly two decades.</p>
<p>Hellraiser, or at least the books and the first movie, have always leaned heavily into sex and BDSM where pain also means pleasure, and judging by the trailer Boss Team Games have kept that element as it begins with a very intimate scene.</p>
<p><iframe title="Clive Barker’s Hellraiser: Revival - Announcement Trailer" width="780" height="439" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/E_4kAp6gsZE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p>


<p>The fact that the game looks so authentic may have something to do with Clive Barker himself being onboard for Hellraiser: Revival.</p>
<p>“Working on the first true Hellraiser game has been a venture deep into the recesses of my darkest imaginings,” said Barker. “The dedication that Saber and Boss Team Games have shown is nothing short of remarkable. They’ve immersed themselves in the Hellraiser universe, capturing its essence—the seductive pull of suffering, the beauty within the grotesque—and forged a narrative that invites players to step beyond the threshold. I’m eager for both the curious and the damned to experience this new chapter in the Hellraiser mythos, where every moment balances on the brink of nightmare and revelation.”</p>

<p>Hellraiser: Revival follows Aiden who must unlock the dark powers of the Genesis Configuration puzzle box and save his girlfriend from the clutches of Pinhead himself. The puzzle box is not just the McGuffin for the game, you can use it to unleash hellish powers while you battle the Cenobites.</p>
